OL,3,CHuge landslide in southwest China
OL,4,Cburies homes and forces over 1,000 to
OL,5,Cevacuate
OL,7,FA landslide in the southwestern
OL,8,FChinese city of Chongqing buried
OL,9,Fresidential buildings, has forced more
OL,10,Fthan 1,100 residents to evacuate and
OL,11,Ftrapping an undetermined number of
OL,12,Fpeople, state media reported.
OL,14,FCCTV said at least ten people were
OL,15,Frescued from the debris and that
OL,16,Fsearch and rescue operations were
OL,17,Fongoing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
