OL,3,CHuge landslide in southwest China
OL,4,Cburies homes and forces over 1,000 to
OL,5,Cevacuate
OL,7,FThe state broadcaster said the
OL,8,Flandslide occurred at around 9.08am in
OL,9,FChongqing's Pengshui County on Friday.
OL,10,FMassive amounts of rocks and soil
OL,11,Fwashed downslope, burying more than
OL,12,Fren residential buildings.
OL,14,FImages from CCTV showed part of a
OL,15,Fmountainside collapsing onto a
OL,16,Fresidential area.
OL,18,FSeveral buildings were located next to
OL,19,Fthe collapse site, while rescue crews
OL,20,Fcombed through the debris.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
