OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784387896
OL,3,CHuge landslide in southwest China
OL,4,Cburies homes and forces over 1,000 to
OL,5,Cevacuate
OL,7,FRescue efforts were hindered by the
OL,8,Funstable terrain and the ongoing risk
OL,9,Fof another landslide, according to the
OL,10,Fbroadcaster.
OL,12,FPhotos showed large slabs of rock
OL,13,Fsliding beside buildings into a
OL,14,Fwaterway below.
OL,16,FTwo buildings that looked about five
OL,17,Fand 15 storeys high were damaged but
OL,18,Fremained standing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
