OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784387896
OL,3,CHuge landslide in southwest China
OL,4,Cburies homes and forces over 1,000 to
OL,5,Cevacuate
OL,7,FThe rain-triggered landslide occurred
OL,8,Fnear a section of the Wujiang River,
OL,9,Fwhich cuts through karst mountains
OL,10,Fpeppered with small towns and terraces.
OL,12,FAuthorities said they sent more than
OL,13,F8,000 disaster-relief items to
OL,14,FChongqing, including tents, folding
OL,15,Fbeds and family emergency kits.
OL,17,FSeveral power poles were buried,
OL,18,Fdisrupting power supplies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
