OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784387896
OL,3,CHuge landslide in southwest China
OL,4,Cburies homes and forces over 1,000 to
OL,5,Cevacuate
OL,7,FWater, electricity and gas supplies
OL,8,Fwere suspended within a half-mile
OL,9,Fradius of the affected area to prevent
OL,10,Ffurther disruptions, authorities said.
OL,12,FPengshui County is located in the
OL,13,Fsoutheast part of Chongqing, bordering
OL,14,Fthe provinces of Hubei and Guizhou.
